Organization = {IEEE; IEEE Comp Soc; IEEE Visualizat \& Graph Tech Comm; InfoVis; SciVis},
Abstract = {In this short paper, we want to give a brief introduction, how we solved
   the 2015 VAST challenge. The main goal was to explain the crime which
   happens in a theme park world called Dinofun. The provided data set
   contains communication and movement data for a three day weekend. During
   the time Scott Jones, a famous fictive soccer star celebrates his
   successes in the park. At one point some criminals vandalized the
   pavilion exhibiting Jones's memorabilia and steal an Olympic medal. In
   this paper we present two special ways to analyze the given data.
   Narrative Charts where used, to show interactions and coordinations
   between different people. Sequence Mining is used to find popular
   attraction combinations.},
