   Springer; Sichuan Univ; Wisesoft Co Ltd},
Abstract = {With the rise of crimes associated with ATM, face occlusion detection
   has gained more and more attention because it facilitates the
   surveillance system of ATM to enhance the safety by pinpointing
   disguised among customers and giving alarms when suspicious customer is
   found. Inspired by strong learning ability of deep learning from data
   and high efficient feature representation ability, this paper proposes a
   cascaded Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) based face occlusion
   detection method. In the proposed method, three cascaded CNNs are used
   to detect head, eye occlusion and mouth occlusion. Experimental results
   show that the proposed method is very effective on two test datasets.},
