Abstract = {The recent economic downturn has made many delinquent credit card
   customers, which in sequence reduced profit margins as well as sales of
   the retail companies. This study focuses on customers who have recovered
   from credit delinquency to analyze repayment patterns of delinquents. A
   Cox regression model is designed as a credit-predicting model to handle
   with credit card debtors. The model predicts the expected time for
   credit recovery from delinquency. The model's prediction accuracy is
   compared with that of other known algorithms.},
