Abstract = {The continuous amalgamation of technology into the ever increasing
   facets of everyday life are conducive to encouraging cyber-crimes and
   cyber-security evolution and diversification. Hence, responses that
   address resulting concerns presented in this mini-track include `A
   Synchronized Shared Key Generation Method for Maintaining End-to-End
   Security of Big Data Streams', `A ThreatVulnerability Based Risk
   Analysis Model for Cyber Physical System Security' and an analysis of
   `How Espoused Culture Influences Misuse Intention: A Micro-Institutional
   Theory Perspective'. These contributions highlight the growing need to
   highlight, investigate and address cyber-security vulnerabilities in the
   broad context of cyber-of-things.},
